        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipes browse — Use-soon toggle</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.recipes-soon-toggle</code> is a pill toggle. Off: neutral bordered surface; On:
        <code>.is-active</code> fills with <code>--color-warning-bg</code> + amber text + no border.
        Timer icon prefix.
