<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipes browse — fulfillment meter (grid)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.fulf-meter</code> is the fulfillment bar used in grid mode: a thin rounded bar
        (filled to <code>pct%</code>, colored by level) + bold percentage text + faint
        "{inStock}/{total} in stock" sub-label. Level color classes: <code>.fulf-hi</code> (≥80%),
        <code>.fulf-mid</code> (≥50%), <code>.fulf-lo</code> (&lt;50%). Applied to both the
        <code>.fulf-meter__bar</code> (via <code>-bg</code> variant) and <code>.fulf-meter__pct</code>.
    </p>
    <div style="max-width:200px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px">
