        (or block-level element) with grid layout. The recipe cell shows a 46px thumb, bold name with
        ellipsis, tag text row, and optional Use-soon badge. The fulfillment cell uses
        <code>.fulf-meter</code>. Cost is omitted when <code>CostCompleteness=None</code>.
    </p>
