        </a>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<div class=\"recipes-grid\">\n  <div class=\"recipes-grid__head\"><!-- 6 col header buttons --></div>\n  <a class=\"recipes-grid__row\" href=\"/Recipes/{id}\">\n    <div class=\"recipes-grid__name-cell\"><!-- thumb + name + tags --></div>\n    <div class=\"fulf-meter\"><!-- bar + pct + sub --></div>\n    <div class=\"recipes-grid__cell recipes-grid__cell--cost num\">{cost}</div>\n    <div class=\"recipes-grid__cell\">{time}</div>\n    <div class=\"recipes-grid__cell\">{serves}</div>\n    <div><svg class=\"icon recipes-grid__chev\">…</svg></div>\n  </a>\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipe detail — back link</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.rd-back</code> — bordered "← All recipes" pill that sits at the top of
        <code>.rd-wrap</code>, above <code>.rd-grid</code>. Rendered as an <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>
        to the browse page; the chevron-right icon is flipped to point left via CSS.
    </p>
    <div style="padding:8px 0">
        <a href="#" class="rd-back">
            <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-chevron-right" /></svg>
            All recipes
        </a>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<a href=\"/Recipes\" class=\"rd-back\">\n  <svg class=\"icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#i-chevron-right\" /></svg>\n  All recipes\n</a>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipe detail — servings stepper</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.recipe-servings-stepper</code> — inline +/− control for the recipe Detail page that
        rescales ingredient quantities client-side via Alpine (J3 step 5). The stepper is wrapped
        in a <code>recipe-meta__item</code> span. Bind <code>x-data</code> at the
        <code>#recipe-detail</code> root with <code>servings</code> and <code>defaultServings</code>
        to drive Alpine's <code>x-text="fmt(baseQty)"</code> on each ingredient quantity span.
    </p>
    <div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:12px 0"
         x-data="{ servings: 4, defaultServings: 4 }">
        <span class="recipe-servings-stepper" role="group" aria-label="Servings">
            <button type="button"
                    class="recipe-servings-stepper__btn"
                    aria-label="Fewer servings"
                    @@click="servings = Math.max(1, servings - 1)"
                    :disabled="servings <= 1">−</button>
            <span class="recipe-servings-stepper__val"
                  x-text="servings + (servings === 1 ? ' serving' : ' servings')">4 servings</span>
            <button type="button"
                    class="recipe-servings-stepper__btn"
                    aria-label="More servings"
                    @@click="servings = servings + 1">+</button>
        </span>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<span class=\"recipe-servings-stepper\" role=\"group\" aria-label=\"Servings\">\n  <button type=\"button\" class=\"recipe-servings-stepper__btn\" aria-label=\"Fewer servings\"\n          @click=\"servings = Math.max(1, servings - 1)\" :disabled=\"servings <= 1\">−</button>\n  <span class=\"recipe-servings-stepper__val\"\n        x-text=\"servings + (servings === 1 ? ' serving' : ' servings')\">4 servings</span>\n  <button type=\"button\" class=\"recipe-servings-stepper__btn\" aria-label=\"More servings\"\n          @click=\"servings = servings + 1\">+</button>\n</span>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipe detail — ingredient status pips</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.ingr-pip</code> — a small colored status dot per ingredient in the Detail page
        fulfillment card (P2-2d). Four states: <code>ingr-pip--instock</code> (green),
        <code>ingr-pip--low</code> (amber), <code>ingr-pip--missing</code> (red),
        <code>ingr-pip--untracked</code> (neutral grey). Rows use <code>.recipe-ingr-pip-row</code>
        with optional <code>.recipe-ingr-pip-row__soon</code> for the Use-soon badge.
    </p>
    <div class="recipe-ingr-pips" style="max-width:340px">
        <div class="recipe-ingr-pip-row" role="listitem">
            <span class="ingr-pip ingr-pip--instock" aria-label="In stock"></span>
            <span class="recipe-ingr-pip-row__name">Rigatoni</span>
        </div>
        <div class="recipe-ingr-pip-row" role="listitem">
            <span class="ingr-pip ingr-pip--low" aria-label="Low"></span>
            <span class="recipe-ingr-pip-row__name">Canned Tomatoes</span>
        </div>
        <div class="recipe-ingr-pip-row" role="listitem">
            <span class="ingr-pip ingr-pip--missing" aria-label="Missing"></span>
            <span class="recipe-ingr-pip-row__name">Garlic Cloves</span>
            <span class="recipe-ingr-pip-row__soon">
                <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-timer" /></svg> Use soon
            </span>
        </div>
        <div class="recipe-ingr-pip-row" role="listitem">
            <span class="ingr-pip ingr-pip--untracked" aria-label="Untracked"></span>
            <span class="recipe-ingr-pip-row__name">Salt <span class="recipe-ingr-pip-row__note">untracked</span></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<div class=\"recipe-ingr-pips\" role=\"list\">\n  <div class=\"recipe-ingr-pip-row\" role=\"listitem\">\n    <span class=\"ingr-pip ingr-pip--instock\" aria-label=\"In stock\"></span>\n    <span class=\"recipe-ingr-pip-row__name\">Product Name</span>\n    <!-- optional: <span class=\"recipe-ingr-pip-row__soon\"><svg …></svg> Use soon</span> -->\n  </div>\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipe detail — cost meta-bar</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.recipe-cost-bar</code> — the cost-per-serving meta-bar for the recipe Detail page
        (P2-2d). Omitted entirely when <code>CostCompleteness=None</code> (never shown as zero, J3).
        When <code>Partial</code>, appends <code>.recipe-cost-bar__estimate</code> (~) and a note line.
        Amount uses <code>var(--font-mono)</code>.
    </p>
    <div>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin-bottom:8px">Full cost:</p>
        <div class="recipe-cost-bar">
            <span class="recipe-cost-bar__label">Cost per serving</span>
            <span class="recipe-cost-bar__amount" style="font-family:var(--font-mono)">$1.40</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--color-text-muted);margin:16px 0 8px">Partial cost:</p>
        <div class="recipe-cost-bar">
            <span class="recipe-cost-bar__label">Cost per serving</span>
            <span class="recipe-cost-bar__amount" style="font-family:var(--font-mono)">
                $0.90 <span class="recipe-cost-bar__estimate" title="Partial cost estimate — 1 ingredient(s) have no price">~</span>
            </span>
            <span class="recipe-cost-bar__note">Estimate — 2 of 3 ingredients priced</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<!-- Full -->\n<div class=\"recipe-cost-bar\">\n  <span class=\"recipe-cost-bar__label\">Cost per serving</span>\n  <span class=\"recipe-cost-bar__amount\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono)\">$1.40</span>\n</div>\n<!-- Partial -->\n<div class=\"recipe-cost-bar\">\n  <span class=\"recipe-cost-bar__label\">Cost per serving</span>\n  <span class=\"recipe-cost-bar__amount\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-mono)\">\n    $0.90 <span class=\"recipe-cost-bar__estimate\" title=\"…\">~</span>\n  </span>\n  <span class=\"recipe-cost-bar__note\">Estimate — 2 of 3 ingredients priced</span>\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

@* ── Recipe Detail — two-column layout components (plantry-v0f) ────────────────── *@

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipe detail — two-column grid (<code>.rd-grid</code>)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.rd-wrap</code> constrains the page to 1180px and provides padding.
        <code>.rd-grid</code> is a two-column grid: <code>1fr 360px</code> (main content + sticky
        action rail). At ≤1080px the grid collapses to a single column and the rail loses its
        sticky positioning. <code>.rd-main</code> is a flex column (gap 20px) for hero + meta + directions.
        <code>.rd-rail</code> is a sticky flex column (gap 16px) for the fulfillment and ingredients cards.
    </p>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<div class=\"rd-wrap\">\n  <div class=\"rd-grid\">\n    <div class=\"rd-main\">\n      <!-- hero, meta strip, directions -->\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rd-rail\">\n      <!-- fulfillment card, ingredients card -->\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipe detail — overlaid hero (<code>.rd-hero</code>)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.rd-hero</code> is a <code>16/9</code> aspect-ratio container. The photo
        (<code>.rd-hero__photo</code>) or themed placeholder (<code>.rd-hero__placeholder</code>)
        fills the full area. A gradient scrim (<code>.rd-hero__scrim</code>) darkens the bottom 65%.
        Name, tags, and source/blurb sit in <code>.rd-hero__info</code> (absolutely positioned,
        z-index 2, anchored to the bottom). Tag mini-pills use <code>.recipe-tag-mini</code>
        (same as gallery cards). The recipe <code>h1</code> gets <code>.rd-hero__name</code>.
        Optional source line uses <code>.rd-hero__blurb</code>.
    </p>
    <div style="max-width:640px">
        <div class="rd-hero" style="aspect-ratio:16/9">
            <div class="rd-hero__placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-recipe" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="rd-hero__scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="rd-hero__info">
                <div class="rd-hero__tags">
                    <span class="recipe-tag-mini">Vegetarian</span>
                    <span class="recipe-tag-mini">Quick</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="rd-hero__name">Tomato Pasta</h1>
                <p class="rd-hero__blurb">Nonna's recipe book</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<div class=\"rd-hero\">\n  <!-- <img class=\"rd-hero__photo\" src=\"…\" alt=\"…\" loading=\"lazy\"> -->\n  <!-- or: <div class=\"rd-hero__placeholder\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg …></svg></div> -->\n  <div class=\"rd-hero__scrim\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n  <div class=\"rd-hero__info\">\n    <div class=\"rd-hero__tags\"><!-- .recipe-tag-mini pills --></div>\n    <h1 class=\"rd-hero__name\">Recipe Name</h1>\n    <p class=\"rd-hero__blurb\">Source / blurb (optional)</p>\n  </div>\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipe detail — meta stat strip (<code>.rd-meta</code>)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.rd-meta</code> is a bordered card containing three equal <code>.rd-meta__cell</code>
        cells separated by hairline dividers. Each cell: icon square (<code>.rd-meta__ico</code>) +
        value/label stack (<code>.rd-meta__val</code> + <code>.rd-meta__lbl</code>). Cells:
        cook time / servings (Alpine-driven) / cost per serving. Cost cell omitted/dimmed when
        <code>CostCompleteness=None</code>. Value uses <code>.rd-meta__val--mono</code> for cost.
        The servings cell's label shows a "scaled N×" note (Alpine <code>x-show="scale !== 1"</code>)
        when the stepper diverges from default.
    </p>
    <div style="max-width:560px">
        <div class="rd-meta" role="list">
            <div class="rd-meta__cell" role="listitem">
                <div class="rd-meta__ico" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg class="icon"><use href="#i-clock" /></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="rd-meta__body">
                    <div class="rd-meta__val">30 min</div>
                    <div class="rd-meta__lbl">Cook time</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rd-meta__cell" role="listitem">
                <div class="rd-meta__ico" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg class="icon"><use href="#i-servings" /></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="rd-meta__body">
                    <div class="rd-meta__val">4 servings</div>
                    <div class="rd-meta__lbl">Yields</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rd-meta__cell" role="listitem">
                <div class="rd-meta__ico" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg class="icon"><use href="#i-tag" /></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="rd-meta__body">
                    <div class="rd-meta__val rd-meta__val--mono">$1.40</div>
                    <div class="rd-meta__lbl">Per serving · $5.60 total</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<div class=\"rd-meta\" role=\"list\">\n  <div class=\"rd-meta__cell\" role=\"listitem\">\n    <div class=\"rd-meta__ico\"><svg class=\"icon\"><use href=\"#i-clock\" /></svg></div>\n    <div class=\"rd-meta__body\">\n      <div class=\"rd-meta__val\">30 min</div>\n      <div class=\"rd-meta__lbl\">Cook time</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- repeat for servings + cost -->\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipe detail — fulfillment rail card (<code>.rd-fulf-card</code>)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        The primary decision card in the rail. Contains: "X of Y ingredients" headline
        (<code>.rd-fulf-headline</code>, count colored by level), "in your pantry right now" sub,
        progress bar (<code>.rd-fulf-bar-wrap</code> + <code>.rd-fulf-bar-fill</code>, filled and
        colored by level class <code>.fulf-hi-bg</code> / <code>.fulf-mid-bg</code> / <code>.fulf-lo-bg</code>),
        breakdown chips (<code>.rd-fulf-chips</code>), optional contextual note
        (<code>.rd-fulf-note--soon</code> or <code>.rd-fulf-note--ready</code>), and action
        buttons (<code>.rd-actions</code>). When fully cookable, add <code>.rd-fulf-card--cookable</code>
        for a subtle green border.
    </p>
    <p>
        Action buttons form a three-tier hierarchy: hero "Cook this" (<code>.btn--cook</code> —
        warm <code>--color-cook</code> fill, larger than the rest), soft "Add N missing"
        (<code>.btn--soft</code>, tinted; disabled when missing=0; behaviour wired by plantry-n2u.2),
        bordered "Edit recipe" (<code>.btn--secondary</code> as <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>).
    </p>
    <div style="max-width:360px">
        <div class="rd-fulf-card">
            <div class="rd-fulf-top">
                <div class="rd-fulf-headline">
                    <span class="rd-fulf-count fulf-mid">2 of 4</span>
                    <span class="rd-fulf-of">ingredients</span>
                </div>
                <div class="rd-fulf-sub">in your pantry right now</div>
                <div class="rd-fulf-bar-wrap" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="50" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
                    <span class="rd-fulf-bar-fill fulf-mid-bg" style="width:50%"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="rd-fulf-chips">
                    <span class="rd-fulf-chip rd-fulf-chip--have"><span class="rd-fulf-chip__dot fulf-hi-bg"></span> 2 in stock</span>
                    <span class="rd-fulf-chip rd-fulf-chip--low"><span class="rd-fulf-chip__dot fulf-mid-bg"></span> 1 running low</span>
                    <span class="rd-fulf-chip rd-fulf-chip--miss"><span class="rd-fulf-chip__dot fulf-lo-bg"></span> 1 to buy</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rd-fulf-note rd-fulf-note--soon" role="note">
                <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-timer" /></svg>
                <span><b>1 ingredient expiring soon.</b> A good reason to cook this now and use them up.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="rd-actions">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn--cook" disabled>
                    <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-flame" /></svg> Cook this
                </button>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn--soft">
                    <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-cart" /></svg> Add 1 missing to shopping list
                </button>
                <a href="#" class="btn btn--secondary">
                    <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-edit" /></svg> Edit recipe
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<div class=\"rd-fulf-card\"><!-- add .rd-fulf-card--cookable when all in stock -->\n  <div class=\"rd-fulf-top\">\n    <div class=\"rd-fulf-headline\">\n      <span class=\"rd-fulf-count fulf-mid\">{inStock} of {total}</span>\n      <span class=\"rd-fulf-of\">ingredients</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rd-fulf-sub\">in your pantry right now</div>\n    <div class=\"rd-fulf-bar-wrap\"><span class=\"rd-fulf-bar-fill fulf-mid-bg\" style=\"width:50%\"></span></div>\n    <div class=\"rd-fulf-chips\"><!-- .rd-fulf-chip--have / --low / --miss --></div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- optional note: .rd-fulf-note--soon or .rd-fulf-note--ready -->\n  <div class=\"rd-actions\">\n    <button class=\"btn btn--cook\">Cook this</button>\n    <button class=\"btn btn--soft\">Add N missing…</button>\n    <a class=\"btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/Recipes/{id}/Edit\">Edit recipe</a>\n  </div>\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Recipe detail — ingredients rail card (<code>.rd-ing-card</code>)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        The ingredient list card in the right rail. Header (<code>.rd-ing-head</code>):
        "Ingredients" h3 + spacer + "Servings" label + servings stepper (<code>.rd-serv-stepper</code>).
        The stepper is an inline +/− control using icon buttons (<code>.rd-serv-stepper__btn</code>)
        and a numeric display (<code>.rd-serv-stepper__val</code>). Alpine binds
        <code>@@click</code> and <code>:disabled</code> on the buttons; <code>x-text="servings"</code>
        on the val. Min=1, max=24.
    </p>
    <p>
        Each ingredient is an <code>.rd-ing-row</code>: status icon box (<code>.rd-ing-status--have / --low / --miss / --untracked</code>)
        + main block (<code>.rd-ing-main</code>: name + optional expiring badge + sub-label) +
        scaled amount (<code>.rd-ing-amt</code>, <code>font-mono</code>, Alpine <code>x-text="fmt(baseQty)"</code>).
        Sub-label class: <code>.rd-ing-sub--have / --low / --miss / --untracked</code>.
    </p>
    <div style="max-width:360px" x-data="{ servings: 4, defaultServings: 4, get scale() { return this.servings / this.defaultServings; }, fmt(qty) { let v = qty * this.scale; return v % 1 === 0 ? v.toString() : v.toPrecision(3).replace(/\\.?0+$/, ''); } }">
        <div class="rd-ing-card">
            <div class="rd-ing-head">
                <h3>Ingredients</h3>
                <div class="rd-ing-head__spacer"></div>
                <span class="rd-serv-stepper__lbl">Servings</span>
                <div class="rd-serv-stepper" role="group" aria-label="Servings">
                    <button type="button" class="rd-serv-stepper__btn" aria-label="Fewer servings"
                            @@click="servings = Math.max(1, servings - 1)" :disabled="servings <= 1">
                        <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-minus" /></svg>
                    </button>
                    <span class="rd-serv-stepper__val" x-text="servings">4</span>
                    <button type="button" class="rd-serv-stepper__btn" aria-label="More servings"
                            @@click="servings = Math.min(24, servings + 1)" :disabled="servings >= 24">
                        <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-plus" /></svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rd-ing-list" role="list">
                <div class="rd-ing-row" role="listitem">
                    <div class="rd-ing-status rd-ing-status--have" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg class="icon"><use href="#i-check" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-main">
                        <div class="rd-ing-name">Rigatoni</div>
                        <div class="rd-ing-sub rd-ing-sub--have">In your pantry</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-amt"><span x-text="fmt(400)">400</span> g</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rd-ing-row" role="listitem">
                    <div class="rd-ing-status rd-ing-status--low" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg class="icon"><use href="#i-alert" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-main">
                        <div class="rd-ing-name">
                            Canned Tomatoes
                            <span class="rd-ing-soon"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-timer" /></svg> 3d</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rd-ing-sub rd-ing-sub--low">Running low</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-amt"><span x-text="fmt(500)">500</span> g</div>
                </div>
                @* rd-ing-soon--expired: danger/red pill for stock that has passed its use-by date (plantry-17n) *@
                <div class="rd-ing-row" role="listitem">
                    <div class="rd-ing-status rd-ing-status--have" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg class="icon"><use href="#i-check" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-main">
                        <div class="rd-ing-name">
                            Double Cream
                            <span class="rd-ing-soon rd-ing-soon--expired"><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-timer" /></svg> Expired 3d ago</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="rd-ing-sub rd-ing-sub--have">In your pantry</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-amt"><span x-text="fmt(200)">200</span> ml</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rd-ing-row" role="listitem">
                    <div class="rd-ing-status rd-ing-status--miss" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg class="icon"><use href="#i-alert" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-main">
                        <div class="rd-ing-name">Garlic Cloves</div>
                        <div class="rd-ing-sub rd-ing-sub--miss">Not in your pantry</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-amt"><span x-text="fmt(3)">3</span> ea</div>
                </div>
                <div class="rd-ing-row" role="listitem">
                    <div class="rd-ing-status rd-ing-status--untracked" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg class="icon"><use href="#i-recipe" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-main">
                        <div class="rd-ing-name">Salt</div>
                        <div class="rd-ing-sub rd-ing-sub--untracked">untracked</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="rd-ing-amt"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<div class=\"rd-ing-card\">\n  <div class=\"rd-ing-head\">\n    <h3>Ingredients</h3>\n    <div class=\"rd-ing-head__spacer\"></div>\n    <span class=\"rd-serv-stepper__lbl\">Servings</span>\n    <div class=\"rd-serv-stepper\" role=\"group\" aria-label=\"Servings\">\n      <button class=\"rd-serv-stepper__btn\" @@click=\"servings=Math.max(1,servings-1)\" :disabled=\"servings<=1\">\n        <svg class=\"icon\"><use href=\"#i-minus\"/></svg></button>\n      <span class=\"rd-serv-stepper__val\" x-text=\"servings\">4</span>\n      <button class=\"rd-serv-stepper__btn\" @@click=\"servings=Math.min(24,servings+1)\" :disabled=\"servings>=24\">\n        <svg class=\"icon\"><use href=\"#i-plus\"/></svg></button>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"rd-ing-list\" role=\"list\">\n    <div class=\"rd-ing-row\" role=\"listitem\">\n      <div class=\"rd-ing-status rd-ing-status--have\"><svg class=\"icon\"><use href=\"#i-check\"/></svg></div>\n      <div class=\"rd-ing-main\">\n        <div class=\"rd-ing-name\">Product Name\n          <!-- optional: <span class=\"rd-ing-soon\"><svg…>timer</svg> 3d</span> -->\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"rd-ing-sub rd-ing-sub--have\">In your pantry</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"rd-ing-amt\"><span x-text=\"fmt(baseQty)\">400</span> g</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

@* ── Shopping List sl-* board components (plantry-ah3) ──────────────────────── *@

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Shopping List — header (<code>.sl-head</code> + <code>.sl-summary</code>)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.sl-head</code> is a flex row: title + subtitle + spacer + <code>.sl-summary</code> stat box.
        The stat box (<code>.ss</code> cells) shows to-buy / checked / total counts; the checked cell gets
        <code>.done</code> to colour its count green (<code>--color-success</code>). All three counts are
        derivable from <code>ShoppingListView.TotalCount</code> and <code>ShoppingListView.CheckedCount</code>.
    </p>
    <div style="max-width: 860px">
        <div class="sl-head">
            <div>
                <h1 style="font-size: 30px; letter-spacing: -0.025em; margin: 0 0 5px; font-weight: 700">Shopping List</h1>
                <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 14.5px">One shared list for your household &middot; grouped by aisle.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="spacer"></div>
            <div class="sl-summary">
                <div class="ss"><div class="n">8</div><div class="l">to buy</div></div>
                <div class="ss done"><div class="n">3</div><div class="l">checked</div></div>
                <div class="ss"><div class="n">11</div><div class="l">total</div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<div class=\"sl-head\">\n  <div>\n    <h1>Shopping List</h1>\n    <p>One shared list for your household · grouped by aisle.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"spacer\"></div>\n  <div class=\"sl-summary\">\n    <div class=\"ss\"><div class=\"n\">@activeCount</div><div class=\"l\">to buy</div></div>\n    <div class=\"ss done\"><div class=\"n\">@checkedCount</div><div class=\"l\">checked</div></div>\n    <div class=\"ss\"><div class=\"n\">@totalCount</div><div class=\"l\">total</div></div>\n  </div>\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Shopping List — add form (<code>.sl-add</code>)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.sl-add</code> is a card wrapping a <code>.sl-add-grid</code> (catalog search | OR divider | custom text input)
        and a <code>.sl-add-foot</code> footer row (qty stepper + unit read-only label + Add button).
        The <code>.sl-or</code> divider renders as a vertical rule with "or" in the centre; at ≤720px it
        collapses to a horizontal rule. The qty stepper uses <code>.sl-qty-stepper</code> + <code>.sl-qbtn</code>
        flanking a number input. Unit is rendered as <code>.sl-qsel-ro</code> (read-only span) until the
        unit-options bead (plantry-dem) lands.
    </p>
    <div style="max-width: 860px">
        <div class="sl-add">
            <div class="sl-add-grid">
                <div class="sl-field">
                    <label><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-search" /></svg> Search catalog</label>
                    <input class="sl-input" placeholder="e.g. Chicken Breast, Spinach…" />
                </div>
                <div class="sl-or"><span>or</span></div>
                <div class="sl-field">
                    <label><svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-edit" /></svg> Custom item</label>
                    <input class="sl-input" placeholder="e.g. Paper towels" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sl-add-foot" x-data="{ qty: 1 }">
                <div class="sl-field">
                    <label>Quantity</label>
                    <div class="sl-qty-stepper">
                        <button type="button" class="sl-qbtn" aria-label="Decrease"
                                @@click="qty = Math.max(0, +(qty - 1).toFixed(2))">
                            <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-minus" /></svg>
                        </button>
                        <input type="number" min="0" step="any" x-model.number="qty" />
                        <button type="button" class="sl-qbtn" aria-label="Increase"
                                @@click="qty = +(qty + 1).toFixed(2)">
                            <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-plus" /></svg>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="sl-field">
                    <label>Unit</label>
                    <span class="sl-qsel-ro">ea</span>
                </div>
                <div class="spacer"></div>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">
                    <svg class="icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="#i-plus" /></svg>
                    Add to list
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <pre class="code-sample"><code>@("<div class=\"sl-add\">\n  <div class=\"sl-add-grid\">\n    <div class=\"sl-field\">\n      <label>Search catalog</label>\n      <!-- searchable-select component -->\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sl-or\"><span>or</span></div>\n    <div class=\"sl-field\">\n      <label>Custom item</label>\n      <input asp-for=\"Input.FreeText\" class=\"sl-input\" placeholder=\"e.g. Paper towels\" maxlength=\"200\" />\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"sl-add-foot\" x-data=\"{ qty: 1 }\">\n    <div class=\"sl-field\">\n      <label>Quantity</label>\n      <div class=\"sl-qty-stepper\">\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"sl-qbtn\" @@click=\"qty = Math.max(0, +(qty-1).toFixed(2))\"><svg class=\"icon\"><use href=\"#i-minus\"/></svg></button>\n        <input asp-for=\"Input.Quantity\" type=\"number\" min=\"0\" step=\"any\" x-model.number=\"qty\" />\n        <button type=\"button\" class=\"sl-qbtn\" @@click=\"qty = +(qty+1).toFixed(2)\"><svg class=\"icon\"><use href=\"#i-plus\"/></svg></button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"sl-field\">\n      <label>Unit</label>\n      <span class=\"sl-qsel-ro\">ea</span>  <!-- read-only until plantry-dem unit-options bead -->\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"spacer\"></div>\n    <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn--primary btn--lg\">Add to list</button>\n  </div>\n</div>")</code></pre>
</section>

<section class="catalog-section">
    <div class="catalog-section__header">
        <h2 class="catalog-section__heading">Shopping List — category group (<code>.sl-group</code>)</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
        <code>.sl-group</code> is a bordered card grouping items by category. The <code>.sl-group-head</code>
        carries a <code>.cdot</code> colour dot (oklch hue from <code>CategoryHue</code>), an uppercase
        category name (<code>h3</code>), and a <code>.count</code> badge. Use the <code>_CatChip</code>
        partial separately for chip-style chips (see the Category chip section above). The dot here is a
        simpler <code>10×10px</code> circle — render with inline <code>style="background: oklch(0.6 0.12 {hue})"</code>.
        For uncategorised items replace the dot with a tag icon.
    </p>
    <div style="max-width: 600px">
        <div class="sl-group" aria-label="Produce">
            <div class="sl-group-head">
                <span class="cdot" style="background: oklch(0.6 0.12 145)" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <h3>Produce</h3>
                <span class="count">3</span>
                <span class="spacer"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="sl-rows">
                <div class="sl-item">
                    <button type="button" class="sl-check" aria-label="Check off Spinach">
